"navVariant":"dark","head":{"title":"Moonstone Advocates | Distinguished Legal Lighthouse in Africa","description":"Kampala-based law firm offering clear, practical legal advice for individuals and businesses. From property to employment, corporate to family law.","ogTitle":"Moonstone Advocates | Distinguished Legal Lighthouse in Africa","ogDescription":"Kampala-based law firm offering clear, practical legal advice for individuals and businesses. From property to employment, corporate to family law.","ogType":"website","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","canonical":"index.html","jsonLd":["{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Kampala Law Firm | MOONSTONE ADVOCATES\",\n  \"description\": \"Kampala-based law firm offering clear, practical legal advice for individuals and businesses. From property to employment, corporate to family law.\",\n  \"url\": \"/\",\n  \"inLanguage\": \"en\",\n  \"about\": {\n    \"@type\": \"LegalService\",\n    \"name\": \"MOONSTONE ADVOCATES\",\n    \"description\": \"Kampala-based law firm offering clear, practical legal advice for individuals and businesses. From property to employment, corporate to family law.\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68f7d32814e72600d0d780d4_Moonstone%20Master%20Logo%20RGB_Black%20Text.svg\"\n    },\n    \"image\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/692f691279c7257ef78ddf7a_hgbj.avif\",\n      \"caption\": \"Reflection of people in a meeting room with blue chairs and a wooden conference table.\"\n    },\n    \"address\": [\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n        \"name\": \"Kampala (Head office)\",\n        \"streetAddress\": \"City Point, 29 King Street\",\n        \"addressLocality\": \"Kampala\",\n        \"postalCode\": \"LS1 2HL\",\n        \"addressCountry\": \"GB\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"telephone\": \"0113 207 0000\",\n    \"areaServed\": \"GB\",\n    \"slogan\": \"Legal expertise. Human inspiration.\",\n    \"founder\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Person\",\n      \"name\": \"Chris Allen\",\n      \"jobTitle\": \"Managing Partner\"\n    },\n    \"aggregateRating\": {\n      \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n      \"ratingValue\": \"5\",\n      \"reviewCount\": \"10\"\n    },\n    \"review\": [\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Holiday & Home Parks Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"Nick helped me through the sale of my family's Holiday Caravan Park & Residential Park. His knowledge of the industry meant that I was guided through everything and I felt like he was always at the end of the phone when I needed him.\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Holiday & Home Parks Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"It has been a real pleasure working with Moonstone – Nick and his team have really helped us in everything from acquiring another holiday park recently to supporting us with complex mobile home act issues. They always react quickly and understand what we are trying to do.\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Holiday & Home Parks Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"I have used Moonstone for matters concerning residents on the park and for the sale of a park. Aimee Hutchinson in particular is an exceptional individual, it's not often you receive feedback/advice out of normal office hours but with her it seems part of the norm which is what I like. The full team in Moonstone seem very competent and I will for sure use them in\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Holiday & Home Parks Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"The team at Moonstone have given us legal advice on a number of occasions. Each team member we've dealt with has been very professional, efficient and helpful.\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Insolvency & Recovery Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"I can't recommend these guys enough. Chris Allen & Ian Scobbie are brilliant, jargon free down to earth advisors. They gave me peace of mind and filled me with confidence in their abilities to deal with our situation. Absolutely give this company a call!\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Landlord Financing & Conveyancing Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"We have used Moonstone for conveyancing 3 times now, as we have found their costs to be reasonable and their service to be excellent. They are very responsive and thorough, which is exactly what you want when navigating the stressful business of buying and selling property.\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Landlord Financing & Conveyancing Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"Moonstone Advocates helped me purchase my first buy to let property. Even though it was a very busy time for the property market, I received consistently thorough information and regular updates, and they made sure everything was clearly explained. I would be happy to work with Moonstone again in the future.\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Corporate Law Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"A special mention to Alex Hall who went above and beyond in her assistance to get our deal over the line. In what ended up being very difficult protracted negotiations, Alex made herself available to us throughout and worked evenings and I am sure some weekends to assist us. She is a very valuable asset to the business, and we cannot speak highly enough of\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Holiday & Home Parks Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"Moonstone LLP are caravan sector experts and have steadily grown their expertise in the sector. They invest in educating themselves in the evolving world of holiday and home park sites.\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Review\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Person\",\n          \"name\": \"Holiday & Home Parks Client\"\n        },\n        \"reviewBody\": \"Nick Dyson has spearheaded the practice in getting to grips with the caravan sector. This doesn't happen overnight and comes through a passion to learn and a willingness to listen.\",\n        \"reviewRating\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Rating\",\n          \"ratingValue\": \"5\"\n        }\n      }\n    ],\n    \"award\": [\n      \"Legal500: Leading Firm\",\n      \"Legal500: Recommended Lawyer\",\n      \"Listed firm 2025: The Lawyer Uganda 200 Rankings\",\n      \"A World Class Company to Work For: Best Companies\",\n      \"World Class Company to Work For: Top Best Law Firm to Work\"\n    ]\n  }\n}"]},"blocks":[{"tag":"main","attrs":{"fade":"target","className":"main-wrapper"},"html":"<header class=\"parallax\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"home-header_content\"><div class=\"padding-section-large max-width-full\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-large\"><h1 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-hero\"><span class=\"yellow\">Legal expertise.</span><br>Human inspiration.</h1></div><div id=\"search-container\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" class=\"home-header_search-form\"></div></div></div><div id=\"search-container\"></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"home-header_signposts\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"home-signpost_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid _30-70_content\"><div data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"_30-70_content-left\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Find the right support for you</h2><p>From corporate law to family matters, our experienced solicitors offer practical, clear advice tailored to your needs.</p></div><div class=\"_30-70_content-right\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid home-signpost_list\"><a hover-wipe=\"trigger\" element-reveal=\"target\" arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" href=\"/for-individuals\" class=\"signpost_link-block w-inline-block\"><div hover-wipe=\"text\" class=\"home-signpost_item\"><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://w