41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div><div class=\"manifesto-middle\"></div><div class=\"manifesto-middle\"></div><div class=\"manifesto-middle\"></div><div data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" id=\"w-node-e6c14649-fd2a-1c42-392a-a543f618ede9-f618edd2\" class=\"manifesto_content-bottom\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><p>With offices in Kampala and London, and led by Managing Partner, Chris Allen since 2008, we bring long standing leadership, consistency, and clear direction to every matter.</p></div><div class=\"manifesto_image-wrapper2\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.05\" alt=\"Modern office reception desk with Moonstone logo and plants behind glass partition.\" src=\"/assets/69f1cbc3a6beb508167d29d4_1761f6882423ea03ed5b0a927acd4fea_Moonstone_under_1mb.jpg\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"manifesto_image2\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></section><div><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Thank you to Danielle for all her effort during this process, obviously not one I wanted to be in, but Danielle has made it a much clearer and less stressful one.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Andrew Pedley was the driving force at Moonstone LLP. He really made us feel like we were the only case on his desk. No job was too small, and no question was too little to ask. He made me feel like my thoughts and views were valid and also explained situations where I wasn&#x27;t understanding the full picture.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Nick helped me through the sale of my family’s Holiday Caravan Park &amp; Residential Park. His knowledge of the industry meant that I was guided through everything and I felt like he was always at the end of the phone when I needed him.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Holiday &amp; Home Parks Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Georgia was incredibly helpful throughout the process of reaching a settlement with a previous employer. Georgia took the time to understand my personal situation and provided clear, considerate, and professional guidance at every stage. Her support made a complex process much easier to navigate, and I felt reassured knowing I was in capable hands.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I used Moonstone for purchasing my property and again years later whilst re-mortgaging, everyone who I spoke to at Moonstone were incredibly knowledgeable and helpful. Beth Hill &amp; Jack Dodd were fantastic at their roles. I would use Moonstone in the future.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Just wanted to say that Danielle&#x27;s helpfulness, generosity of time, and straightforward way of discussing things so far have already been really refreshing regarding this awkward process. It is really appreciated.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Paula was brilliant throughout, providing help, support and advice during an incredibly long and drawn-out situation that should never have reached that point in the first place. I’m truly grateful for everything she did.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone provided an excellent, comprehensive service when drawing up my will and Lasting Power Attorney. Emily Owston was professional and answered all of my questions.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Chris is a great listener, clear communicator and, in my opinion, a genuinely good, kind human being. I have no hesitation in recommending Moonstone in Kampala for any legal matters you may have; you&#x27;ll be in good hands.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I have dealt with Chris Allen recently concerning some rather upsetting and extremely delicate matters. Chris and the team have proved to be reassuring, down to earth and absolute consummate professionals.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"section_home_blog\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"home_blog_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid home_blog_content\"><div class=\"home_blog_content-left\"><div class=\"max-width-small max-width-full-tablet\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Updates that matter to you</h2><p>Stay informed with guidance and insights from our specialists - helping you make confident decisions at home, at work, and across your business.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a data-theme=\"light\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"/insight-hub\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg light\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle light\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text light\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">View all insights</p></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"home_blog_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"home_blog_list w-dyn-items\"><div element-reveal=\"target\" data-w-id=\"1f53414d-a146-3a78-dc06-42bc7906ca8a\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"home_blog_item w-dyn-item\"><a list-link=\"trigger\" hover-zoom=\"trigger\" href=\"/insight-hub/blog/employment-rights-act-update-what-business-owners-need-to-know\" class=\"home_blog_item-link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"home_blog_image-wrapper\"><img hover-zoom=\"target\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/69eb76b9fcc8ba17e444975f_dylan-gillis-KdeqA3aTnBY-unsplash.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"/assets/69eb76b9fcc8ba17e444975f_dylan-gillis-KdeqA3aTnBY-unsplash-p-500.jpg 500w, /assets/69eb76b9fcc8ba17e444975f_dylan-gillis-KdeqA3aTnBY-unsplash-p-800.jpg 800w, /assets/69eb76b9fcc8ba17e444975f_dylan-gillis-KdeqA3aTnBY-unsplash-p-1080.jpg 1080w, /assets/69eb76b9fcc8ba17e444975f_dylan-gillis-KdeqA3aTnBY-unsplash.jpg 1200w\" class=\"image\"></div><div class=\"home_blog_item-content\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><div class=\"article-meta\"><div class=\"secondary_tag\">Employment</div></div></div><h5 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Employment Rights Act update: What business owners need to know</h5><div class=\"text-weight-normal\">The Employment Rights Act 2025 introduces major workplace reforms from 2026. Learn what the key changes mean for employers and how businesses should prepare.</div><div class=\"margin-top margin-small\"><div list-link=\"trigger\" class=\"button is-text-link is-inl